  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Raiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 10 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 23</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, S, E, F, Mas</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You channel the power of a chidori into a weapon with a Containment seal, allowing its attacks to ignore 10 hardness, 2 points of armor or shield bonus to Defense, and make it deal 1d6 electric bonus damage on hit (not multiplied on critical hits). Attacks made count as Chakra enhanced to bypass damage reduction.<br><br>As a swift action, the technique can be dismissed to deal 1d6 electric damage to a creature within 10 feet, forcing them to make a save to avoid being @Condition[staggered;duration=1]{staggered} for 1 round and being knocked @Condition[prone]{prone}. If the weapon loses contact with your hand for more than one round, the technique ends.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The third step lets you spend 4 Chakra to have the weapon deal 1d10 electric damage on critical hits, and add 1d6 concussion damage when discharged.<br><br>The fifth step lets you spend 2 Chakra to increase the damage on hit to 1d10, and increase the damage on discharge by 1d6 electric.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
